Package org.hayabaya Description

Haybaya java profiling project for benchmarking performance of the Java Virtual Machine

Hayabaya is a benchmarking tool for measuring the performance of the basic arithmetic operations primitive java arrays. The primitive data types float, integer, long and double are profiled together with their boxed counterparts.

Since:
1.0.0
